  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/68c13d10204eb2b79f97a3409f7cb08c.webp?t=1757651493\" width=600 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/e3c90c6edfcca5adbe9fbd7968643b4c.poster.avif?t=1757651493\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/e3c90c6edfcca5adbe9fbd7968643b4c.webm?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/e3c90c6edfcca5adbe9fbd7968643b4c.mp4?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you will have to take on the role of Monster Merchant. Amazingly cute creatures roam the neighborhood, catch them, sell them! This is your job, try not to think about it too much, take your medicine, get enough sleep and get back to work.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/4179fb52da3902427ea5baf1785e06c0.webp?t=1757651493\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/5c04a49ff71586dc3f01ede119e4e0bf.poster.avif?t=1757651493\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/5c04a49ff71586dc3f01ede119e4e0bf.webm?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/5c04a49ff71586dc3f01ede119e4e0bf.mp4?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell creatures, and use the proceeds to buy improvements for the farm and capture tools, and open new zones to hunt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 20 cute creatures to capture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unlockable areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story with a twist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy and relaxing gameplay</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/68c13d10204eb2b79f97a3409f7cb08c.webp?t=1757651493\" width=600 height=55 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/e3c90c6edfcca5adbe9fbd7968643b4c.poster.avif?t=1757651493\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/e3c90c6edfcca5adbe9fbd7968643b4c.webm?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/e3c90c6edfcca5adbe9fbd7968643b4c.mp4?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you will have to take on the role of Monster Merchant. Amazingly cute creatures roam the neighborhood, catch them, sell them! This is your job, try not to think about it too much, take your medicine, get enough sleep and get back to work.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/4179fb52da3902427ea5baf1785e06c0.webp?t=1757651493\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/5c04a49ff71586dc3f01ede119e4e0bf.poster.avif?t=1757651493\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/5c04a49ff71586dc3f01ede119e4e0bf.webm?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442580/extras/5c04a49ff71586dc3f01ede119e4e0bf.mp4?t=1757651493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell creatures, and use the proceeds to buy improvements for the farm and capture tools, and open new zones to hunt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 20 cute creatures to capture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unlockable areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story with a twist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy and relaxing gameplay</p></li></ul>",
